talks with Sudanese President Omar al-Bashir on Libya's role in
the reconciliation between the Sudanese government and opposition.
</P>
<P>
Seeing Gaddafi off at the airport, al-Bashir said Gaddafi's
visit was successful in dealing with African and Arab issues.
</P>
<P>
However, Gaddafi made no comment on the visit.
</P>
<P>
Observers here noted that Gaddafi paid a surprise visit to
Sudan and left Sudan silently.
</P>
<P>
