saying "The Arabs must unify their African Arab nation and
determine their destiny."
</P>
<P>
He stressed the importance of stopping the bloodshed in south
Sudan and reconciling the Sudanese government with the opposition
to stop the civil war and establish peace.
</P>
<P>
The two sides also signed an accord on bilateral cooperation
and pledged to hold a higher joint ministerial commission in Libya
next September. 
