<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, June 21 (Xinhua) -- British Foreign Secretary Robin
Cook said Monday that his Russian counterpart Igor Ivanov would
visit Britain next month to help strengthen ties between the two
nations.
</P>
<P>
"I can confirm that (Ivanov) has agreed to my invitation to
visit Britain next month as my personal guest, and we will explore
how to strengthen Britain and Russian relations," Cook told a
