<HEADLINE> Filipino Driver Eyes Honors at Asian Formula 2000 in China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, June 21 (Xinhua) -- Champion driver Richard Joson hopes
to achieve no other Filipino has done before when he represents
the country in the third and fourth rounds of the Asian Formula
2000 to be held on June 27 at the Zhuhai Circuit in China.
</P>
