<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Closes Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, June 21 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange on Monday closed at 1,718.90 points, up 0.41 points
from Sunday's finish.
</P>
