government's Digital 21st century IT strategy is to raise the
awareness, confidence and familiarity of the community in the use
of IT in all spheres of their lives.
</P>
<P>
"To this end, we have joined hands with other organizations and
government departments to promote the wider use of IT and the
adoption of E-commerce," he added.
</P>
