to 9.73 Australian dollars, ANZ bank eased 8.1 to 11.12 Australian
dollars, National Australia Bank surrendered four cents to 26.00
Australian dollars and Commonwealth bank slipped 1.6 to 25.00
Australian dollars.
</P>
