the completion of their withdrawal from Kosovo. French troops
observed the pullout of the last group of the Yugoslav troops and
police forces from Kosovo. NATO confirmed the pullout of all
Yugoslav forces and announced a definite ending of its bombing
campaign against Belgrade.
</P>
