that only the anti-Kabila rebel Rally for Democracy in Congo (RCD)
will sign the peace agreement and non-combatant opposition
parties from the Democratic Republic of Congo (DRC) will not be
part of the ceasefire accord to be signed here next Saturday at a
regional summit. 
