<HEADLINE> Private Dwellings Selling Well In Northern China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIANJIN, June 21 (Xinhua) -- North China's port city of Tianjin
had 1,600 private housing deals covering 110,000 square meters of
living space in the first five months of this year, up 20 percent
from last year's corresponding period.
</P>
