<HEADLINE> Germany Ties Italy in Women's World Cup </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PASADENA, California, June 20 (Xinhua) -- Bettina Wiegmann
scored a penalty kick to help Germany salvage a 1-1 tie with Italy
in a Women's World Cup Group B match here on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Germany, beaten finalists in the 1995 World Cup, fell behind in
the first half on a 36th minute Patrizia Panico goal.
</P>
