<HEADLINE> Brazil Beats Canada in Volleyball World League </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
RIO DE JENAIRO, June 20 (Xinhua) -- Brazil scored a straight-
set victory over Canada here on Sunday, setting solid foundation
for entering the second phase of the Men's Volleyball World League.
